title: Classic Interview ( Souljah Boy and Tiffany Haddish)
itunes:title: Classic Interview ( Souljah Boy and Tiffany Haddish)
description:
This episode we flashed back to the first time Souljah Boy visited The Breakfast Club, and said the classic and viral line "DRAKE" , spoke about how so many other rappers stole his flow and material, Also we flashed back to the classic interview with comedian Tiffany Haddish stopped by the show and spoke about the time she left some droppings in her then boyfriends sneaker after she found out he cheated, talk about revenge!
